eplyTime":"2017-11-02T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"成日都見好多人排<br />\n未食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecce5255cefb55c1d37e6ad540c5b3cc70dc636","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一般 <br />\n只係荃灣個陣無乜咁嘅cafe係當眼處 比佢做左先</blockquote><br />\n老細話自己係天才，死位，死場，比佢打救返生"},{"pid":"fdd23336de44b489f473754a3226e3104f9bcdb3","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲嘢又貴又少，唔係特別好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估佢地有冇即場厨師煮？"},{"pid":"99a3a4ac47efc92213a94ea015fa0d6e7218cd8e","tid":455340,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一般 <br />\n只係荃灣個陣無乜咁嘅cafe係當眼處 比佢做左先</blockquote><br />\n老細話自己係天才，死位，死場，比佢打救返生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理撚得佢 總之啲野一般"},{"pid":"89ce887e5126dfa526751ecbeb59472dfde20d3a","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"其實而家開 cafe , 根starfuck 咁，食物全中央厨房交貨去店內翻熱"},{"pid":"277573ee059b0f3b96d961eadc7cddf38047723c","tid":455340,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2596385a83305497d425ff8a2bbb453896db2924","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而家開 cafe , 根starfuck 咁，食物全中央厨房交貨去店內翻熱</blockquote><br />\n最大成本係裝修，比到個 feel 出黎，<br />\n<br />\n員工係最唔重要，老細自己話對住班讀書唔成既垃圾用下威嚇手段，唔聽話，即炒唔賠，長期請人攞定reference 可以隨時叫到人頂。班友怕炒就多數都貼貼服服<br />\n<br />\n就算玩野唔撈佢隨時叫到人唔怕佢地玩野。<br />\n<br />\n佢而家全港開左四 五間分店ing"},{"pid":"d7845e548ce030fd19e387010b73903980914c8b","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實而家開 cafe , 根starfuck 咁，食物全中央厨房交貨去店內翻熱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中央廚房是咩來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n在工廠集中整好"},{"pid":"730c7246987c7ea91910d72336882a03d76acba8","tid":455340,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:11:21.000Z","msg":"好難食"},{"pid":"29163251dfb28a3965da7e7288b11c351cd3b535","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實而家開 cafe , 根starfuck 咁，食物全中央厨房交貨去店內翻熱</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中央廚房是咩來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔駛做個厨房請厨師 cfu ，做飲食最重要個chief。<br />\n<br />\n而家真係易做好多"},{"pid":"bb22ea924ecec7e1a8d68a5bb69ef2d293b569b3","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難食</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，佢狂賺錢喎<br />\n<br />\n我都想開"},{"pid":"61da8ffe82f0355d5c3fe2cc5a89caecdde56a2d","tid":455340,"uid":27766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好難食</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，佢狂賺錢喎<br />\n<br />\n我都想開</blockquote><br />\n我唔知你係咪假膠<br />\n<br />\n但好食同賺錢好似冇邏輯關係"},{"pid":"5174f1c952ad90eb606abd77b9cf7a05ca82f6b4","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好難食</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，佢狂賺錢喎<br />\n<br />\n我都想開</blockquote><br />\n我唔知你係咪假膠<br />\n<br />\n但好食同賺錢好似冇邏輯關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點假腸？<br />\n<br />\n食物唔好食，食店會賺大錢，係乜財妓，teach me thx"},{"pid":"c5b44668d41c54863ae462b6d54a11f396987a94","tid":455340,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f4c5e9ce8640043580512e4e351d0cb7bc98bed","tid":455340,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:23:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43d8c22161ca94d933ceccc465cf41d6e1708392","tid":455340,"uid":10219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實而家開 cafe , 根starfuck 咁，食物全中央<span style=\"color: red;\">厨</span>房交貨去店內翻熱</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddae13d11e77cb80ffac9d1760e13e01bb9a75b2","tid":455340,"uid":45684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:26:49.000Z","msg":"樓主真心想搞人，留名食花生"},{"pid":"a5b83f27fce8750b5b5de053d65cba797e501ebf","tid":455340,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好難食</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，佢狂賺錢喎<br />\n<br />\n我都想開</blockquote><br />\n我唔知你係咪假膠<br />\n<br />\n但好食同賺錢好似冇邏輯關係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點假腸？<br />\n<br />\n食物唔好食，食店會賺大錢，係乜財妓，teach me thx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，你係咪喺香港住㗎？垃圾質素的餐廳，不便宜的價錢，都大把人食啦，洗能財技咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌，我唔出街食野架。鳩知咩。只係見認間野個老細好後生，死場都月月執廿萬，想學下佢姐"}]}